about.description: I started education in 1999. I graduated from high school in 2011 and graduated from Istanbul University Faculty of Communication in 2016. In the same years, I started my music life in TRT Istanbul Radio Youth Choir. I performed great works such as the 9th Symphony on stages such as Zorlu PSM and Lütfi Kırdar with IDSO. Between 2017-2020, I was engaged in automobile trade. In 2020-2022, I worked in the field of software. With 2023, I have been working in the field of SEO, Ads and software.
